rows.label: tlk00340104_msg0001
rows.name: Safe journey. Fons Maim's a way out.

rows.label: tlk00340104_msg0002
rows.name:
And the monsters are tough as old
nails out there. Make sure you're all
set before you head out, yeah?

rows.label: tlk00340104_msg0003
rows.name:
When in doubt, just bear the Boss's
words in mind. He'll keep you in good
stead.
